{
  "rootDuration": 230.5,
  "audioDuration": 230.380958,
  "segments": [
    {
      "scene": 1,
      "text": "同学你好，这一节我们学习七年级上册第三章，一元一次方程。",
      "caption": "这一节学习：七年级上册第三章，一元一次方程。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/01.wav",
      "duration": 4.903417,
      "start": 0,
      "end": 4.903417
    },
    {
      "scene": 1,
      "text": "这一章会帮你把文字问题翻译成方程，再把方程一步一步解出来。",
      "caption": "把文字问题翻译成方程，再一步一步解出来。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/02.wav",
      "duration": 5.618,
      "start": 5.043417,
      "end": 10.661417
    },
    {
      "scene": 1,
      "text": "我们重点抓三件事：什么是方程，怎样检验方程的解，以及怎样解一元一次方程。",
      "caption": "本章重点：方程、方程的解、解一元一次方程。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/03.wav",
      "duration": 8.179167,
      "start": 10.801417,
      "end": 18.980584
    },
    {
      "scene": 2,
      "text": "先看方程，含有未知数的等式叫做方程。",
      "caption": "先看方程：含有未知数的等式叫做方程。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/04.wav",
      "duration": 3.858208,
      "start": 19.380584,
      "end": 23.238792
    },
    {
      "scene": 2,
      "text": "比如一个数加五等于十二，设这个数为 x，就可以写成 x 加五等于十二。",
      "caption": "一个数加 5 等于 12，可以写成 x + 5 = 12。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/05.wav",
      "duration": 6.727708,
      "start": 23.378792,
      "end": 30.1065
    },
    {
      "scene": 2,
      "text": "注意，只有式子含有未知数还不够，它还必须是等式。",
      "caption": "只有未知数还不够，它还必须是等式。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/06.wav",
      "duration": 4.898,
      "start": 30.2465,
      "end": 35.1445
    },
    {
      "scene": 3,
      "text": "什么叫一元一次方程？只含有一个未知数，并且未知数的次数是 1 的方程，叫做一元一次方程。",
      "caption": "一元一次方程：一个未知数，次数是 1。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/07.wav",
      "duration": 9.696083,
      "start": 35.5445,
      "end": 45.240583
    },
    {
      "scene": 3,
      "text": "比如三 x 等于十八、二 x 减七等于九，都是一元一次方程。",
      "caption": "3x = 18 和 2x - 7 = 9 都是一元一次方程。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/08.wav",
      "duration": 5.865125,
      "start": 45.380583,
      "end": 51.245708
    },
    {
      "scene": 3,
      "text": "但 x 加 y 等于十有两个未知数，x 平方等于九次数不是一，所以都不符合。",
      "caption": "x + y = 10 和 x² = 9 都不符合。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/09.wav",
      "duration": 8.659292,
      "start": 51.385708,
      "end": 60.045
    },
    {
      "scene": 4,
      "text": "方程的解，是让左右两边相等的未知数的值。",
      "caption": "方程的解：让左右两边相等的未知数的值。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/10.wav",
      "duration": 4.578042,
      "start": 60.445,
      "end": 65.023042
    },
    {
      "scene": 4,
      "text": "检验时，把这个数代入原方程的左边和右边分别计算。",
      "caption": "检验要代回原方程，左右两边分别计算。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/11.wav",
      "duration": 5.140917,
      "start": 65.163042,
      "end": 70.303959
    },
    {
      "scene": 4,
      "text": "例如 x 加五等于十二，代入 x 等于七，左边是七加五等于十二，右边也是十二，所以七是这个方程的解。",
      "caption": "x = 7 时，7 + 5 = 12，左右相等。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/12.wav",
      "duration": 13.142125,
      "start": 70.443959,
      "end": 83.586084
    },
    {
      "scene": 4,
      "text": "只看算出来像不像答案是不够的，代回原方程才稳。",
      "caption": "只看答案不够，代回原方程才稳。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/13.wav",
      "duration": 5.305,
      "start": 83.726084,
      "end": 89.03108399999999
    },
    {
      "scene": 5,
      "text": "接下来学习解一元一次方程，我们的目标，是把方程变形成 x 等于某个数。",
      "caption": "解方程目标：把方程变形成 x = a。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/14.wav",
      "duration": 7.214792,
      "start": 89.431084,
      "end": 96.645876
    },
    {
      "scene": 5,
      "text": "常用顺序是：去括号、移项、合并同类项、系数化为一。",
      "caption": "常用顺序：去括号、移项、合并同类项、系数化为 1。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/15.wav",
      "duration": 9.382792,
      "start": 96.785876,
      "end": 106.168668
    },
    {
      "scene": 5,
      "text": "每一步都依据等式性质，方程两边同时做同样的运算，等式仍然成立。",
      "caption": "等式性质：两边同时做同样运算，等式仍然成立。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/16.wav",
      "duration": 9.295833,
      "start": 106.308668,
      "end": 115.604501
    },
    {
      "scene": 6,
      "text": "看第一个例题，文具费用：一本练习本三元，又买一支五元的笔，一共花二十元，问买了几本练习本。",
      "caption": "例题：一本练习本 3 元，一支笔 5 元，总共 20 元。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/17.wav",
      "duration": 8.66525,
      "start": 116.004501,
      "end": 124.669751
    },
    {
      "scene": 6,
      "text": "设买了 x 本，练习本费用就是三 x 元。",
      "caption": "设买了 x 本，练习本费用就是 3x 元。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/18.wav",
      "duration": 5.061167,
      "start": 124.809751,
      "end": 129.87091800000002
    },
    {
      "scene": 6,
      "text": "等量关系是：练习本费用加笔的费用，等于总费用，所以列方程三 x 加五等于二十。",
      "caption": "练习本费用 + 笔的费用 = 总费用，列方程 3x + 5 = 20。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/19.wav",
      "duration": 9.293083,
      "start": 130.010918,
      "end": 139.304001
    },
    {
      "scene": 6,
      "text": "移项得三 x 等于十五，两边同时除以三，得到 x 等于五。",
      "caption": "移项得 3x = 15，两边除以 3，得到 x = 5。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/20.wav",
      "duration": 6.894208,
      "start": 139.444001,
      "end": 146.33820899999998
    },
    {
      "scene": 6,
      "text": "检验一下，三乘五再加五等于二十，所以答案是五本。",
      "caption": "检验：3×5+5=20，所以答案是 5 本。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/21.wav",
      "duration": 6.960333,
      "start": 146.47820899999996,
      "end": 153.43854199999996
    },
    {
      "scene": 7,
      "text": "再看一个未知数在两边的例题：左边有二 x 加四个座位，右边有 x 加十六个座位，左右相同。",
      "caption": "例题：左边 2x + 4，右边 x + 16，左右相同。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/22.wav",
      "duration": 11.54025,
      "start": 153.83854199999996,
      "end": 165.37879199999998
    },
    {
      "scene": 7,
      "text": "列出方程：二 x 加四等于 x 加十六。",
      "caption": "列出方程：2x + 4 = x + 16。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/23.wav",
      "duration": 5.222667,
      "start": 165.51879199999996,
      "end": 170.74145899999996
    },
    {
      "scene": 7,
      "text": "把右边的 x 移到左边，把左边的四移到右边，注意移项要变号。",
      "caption": "移项要变号：右边的 x 到左边，左边的 4 到右边。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/24.wav",
      "duration": 6.7335,
      "start": 170.88145899999995,
      "end": 177.61495899999994
    },
    {
      "scene": 7,
      "text": "得到二 x 减 x 等于十六减四，所以 x 等于十二。",
      "caption": "得到 2x - x = 16 - 4，所以 x = 12。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/25.wav",
      "duration": 6.813333,
      "start": 177.75495899999993,
      "end": 184.56829199999993
    },
    {
      "scene": 8,
      "text": "本章最容易错的地方有三个。第一，把不是等式的式子也当成方程；第二，忘记检查未知数个数和次数。",
      "caption": "易错点：不是等式也当方程；忘记检查未知数个数和次数。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/26.wav",
      "duration": 9.138792,
      "start": 184.96829199999993,
      "end": 194.10708399999993
    },
    {
      "scene": 8,
      "text": "第三，移项只移动位置却忘记变号。",
      "caption": "第三：移项只移动位置，却忘记变号。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/27.wav",
      "duration": 3.946167,
      "start": 194.24708399999992,
      "end": 198.19325099999992
    },
    {
      "scene": 8,
      "text": "解完以后，把答案代回原方程检验，能帮你抓住很多符号错误。",
      "caption": "解完代回原方程检验，能抓住很多符号错误。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/28.wav",
      "duration": 5.5405,
      "start": 198.3332509999999,
      "end": 203.8737509999999
    },
    {
      "scene": 9,
      "text": "最后记住一条主线：找等量关系，列方程，按步骤求解，再代回检验。学完这一章，你要能从实际问题里设未知数、列方程，并稳稳地解出一元一次方程。",
      "caption": "主线：找等量关系，列方程，求解，再检验。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/29.wav",
      "duration": 18.663917,
      "start": 204.27375099999992,
      "end": 222.93766799999992
    },
    {
      "scene": 9,
      "text": "现在回到软件里完成第三章单元小测，看看自己能不能把方程用起来。",
      "caption": "回到软件里完成第三章单元小测。",
      "file": "/Users/vic/Downloads/初中数学Ai教学/chapter-videos/g7-shang-unit-3-yi-yuan-yi-ci-fang-cheng/assets/sentence-segments-smooth-female-teacher-v2/trimmed/30.wav",
      "duration": 6.503292,
      "start": 223.0776679999999,
      "end": 229.5809599999999
    }
